dct_description_sm: California shown as a long, labeled island with no place names and an indented northern coast.
Title in banner across top. Decorative border around map. "156" at top left. "259" at top right.
Partial coastlines of New Zealand and Australia are shown. The Great Lakes are complete. The Great Wall of China is shown. Includes small ships and compass roses.
